OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FIndia opposition criticises
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FModi for 'hate speech'     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, India's opposition has accused PM      
OL,6, Narendra Modi of Islamophobic remarks  
OL,7, after he claimed his opponents would   
OL,8, distribute people's wealth to          
OL,9, "infiltrators" if they won power.      
OL,11,FMr Modi told a rally the opposition    
OL,12,FCongress wanted to distribute wealth to
OL,13,F"those who have many children".        
OL,15,FHis remarks were widely seen as        
OL,16,Freferring to India's Muslim minority.  
OL,18,FThe Congress party has rejected the    
OL,19,Fclaim, which came days after the       
OL,20,Fgeneral election began.                
